Text: WORSE MOVIES EVER MADE IN THE ENTIRE HISTORY OF HOLLYWOOD
Indeed! This is bad, really bad. It kinda pisses me of as they mess with the "not another" concept and then put up this crap instead.

I'm Astonished that good or decent actors like Burt Reynolds and Vinnie Jones agreed to this piece of shit film, i mean why would you agree to star in a film after reading a script that a 5 year old kid could write better jokes into ? clearly they must have been paid LOTS of cash and have decided to ruin their career by doing this, good luck wasting 99 minutes of your life. 

A-10
